*Send a tx file through STARSIM
MACRO StarSim inputFile outputFile nEvents detectorGeometry 

*Set Debug Mode on/off
DEBUG on

*Open the Output File
USER/OUTPUT o [outputFile].fzd

*Set Geometry
DETP geom [detectorGeometry]

*Create Geometry
gexe $STAR_LIB/xgeometry.so
*MAKE geometry

*Set the input file
USER/INPUT TX [inputFile]

*Number of Events
trig [nEvents]

*Close Output File
USER/OUTPUT c [outputFile].fzd

*Exit from STARSIM
exit